## Typical names of GNU standard readme files:
##
##   +--------------+----------------------+--------------------+--------------------------------------------+
##   |filename      |file to use instead   |required by         |comment                                     |      
##   +--------------+----------------------+--------------------+--------------------------------------------+
##   +--------------+----------------------+--------------------+--------------------------------------------+
##   |ABOUT-GNU     |                      |                    |outdated                                    |
##   |              |                      |                    |                                            |
##   |              |                      |                    |can no longer be found on the internet      |
##   +--------------+----------------------+--------------------+--------------------------------------------+
##   |ABOUT-NLS     |                      |                    |outdated                                    |
##   |              |                      |                    |                                            |
##   |              |                      |                    |a file from GNU gettext                     |
##   +--------------+----------------------+--------------------+--------------------------------------------+
##   |AUTHORS       |                      |required by GNU     |contains credits to the package authors     |
##   |              |                      |                    |                                            |
